16 May 2015The Inter-Ministerial Committee (IMC) on migration led by Minister for Performance, Monitoring and Evaluation in the Presidency, Mr Jeff Radebe will hold a media briefing to provide an update on its work.Details of the briefing are as follows:Date: Sunday, 17 May 2015 Time: 10h00 Venue: GCIS, Tshedimosetso House, Corner Francis Baard and Festival streets, Hatfield PretoriaNB: There will be a video link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, and Parliament in Cape TownRSVP: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) Cell: 082 440 5676 Andile Duka (Cape Town) Cell: 071 154 5619Enquiries: Acting Cabinet Spokesperson Phumla Williams Cell: 083 501 0139Issued by the Government Communication and Information Systems (GCIS)